{"type": "article", "id": 29582, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-13T23:08:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27756, "name": "NEMO"}, {"id": 30143, "name": "Fuksas"}, {"id": 30144, "name": "José Lévy"}, {"id": 30145, "name": "Jaebum Joo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607131636124v8Q32YdPslSDJmi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Olympia by Nemo</h3><p>灯具品牌 <a href=\"http://nemolighting.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nemo</a> 最新推出 Olympia 是一个极简而抽象的灯具系列，由 <a href=\"http://www.fuksas.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fuksas</a> 工作室的 Doriana 和 Massimiliano Fuksas 共同设计完成。黑白相间的柔光罩借鉴了飞碟的造型，亮灯后会让光线产生 360 度的发散，看上去就好像悬浮在空中一样，透露出一股神秘的气息。灯罩通过活动长臂与底座相连，可以根据需要自由调节，适用于各种不同的环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225731mr4JzKW1vdgayLUn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.436430\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225731SH6eDKNEBUGIVz3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225732m3FQ4CeGRTA9JUvg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132257310sWz54ZCUNpGDFhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.916870\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132257328MjHVtwas9qlL4BR.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.970660\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225732KaBLXlQPgD4YyFHG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.239609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Camera Lift-Strap by PONTE Leather Co.</h3><p>我们都希望在旅行时记录下那些特别的瞬间，然而扛着沉重的相机很容易对颈椎和肩膀造成损伤。为了缓解相机对身体的重压，美国 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PONTEleatherco/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PONTE Leather</a> 公司专门设计了一款名为 Life-Strap 的背带。它在后颈处附有一个额外的扣环，能够与背包的提手相连，让受力面更均匀地分布在后背。背带自适应的设计可以用于任何相机，哪怕是古董机也能够利用特制的金属环进行调节。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ponteleather/camera-lift-strap-explore-and-capture-comfortably\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，帆布款和皮革款的最低价分别为 26 和 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225659Qp8qofwCPEib05xv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225659MQghVEr2Lq9SY0le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132256594qS5U8CYwgyGB7jh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677467\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132256593jKXI5plFi7HYcVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225700wB7Ao0sPS4RMkzi9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Moving Tatami by José Lévy</h3><p>在法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.joselevy.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">José Lévy</a> 眼中，榻榻米不仅可以作为地板铺就，也可以成为家具的设计元素起到装饰的效果。Moving Tatami 就是他为日本制造商 <a href=\"http://www.daiken-ad.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daiken</a> 设计的一套家具，包含了沙发、储物柜、边桌、架子。部分表面由榻榻米覆盖，搭配上漆的木材显得十分素颜。为了增强榻榻米的耐用性，Lévy 在制作时还加入了和纸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225639cCh768vSAfXLxHPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225639aNDYMuc9SsIxWQig.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132256392FKam5BArpGbf4hz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132256404JPKHCTySb1LNirt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225640nu8c0BIZXxigHD3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PIXU by mavcdesign</h3><p>要在拼图上玩出花样，或许没有比像素风更合适的了。来自韩国的 <a href=\"http://www.mavcdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mavcdesign</a> 最近同像素艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.joojaebum.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jaebum Joo</a> 联手打造了一套 8-bit 风格的拼图 PIXU，分为自画像和名画两种款式：Joo 会根据你提供的照片绘制出像素头像，再由 mavcdesign 制作出相应的拼图；名画系列则包含了《星空》、《呐喊》、《蒙娜丽莎》等六幅画作的迷你拼图。虽然 PIXU 的成品并不大，但这种独特的风格搭配个性化的定制实在是种草能力十足。值得一提的是，自画像更是限量 550 人。如果你对这个拼图感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mavcdesign/pixu-on-demand-brick-pixel-portrait\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，自画像款和名画款的早鸟价分别为 24 和 44 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225603jI2rLtlmxhiKGVYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225601whgqbro7zCyvU3nQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225602MKou7EwbjWUQPda6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225601IpsNFqVl9k6CQUbD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132256023S4e1cTI2rAmBoRJ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225601zrdYmxF7hH16bRL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GravityFlow 2 by Craig Wenger &amp; David Turover</h3><p>养鱼最麻烦的莫过于换水和清洗鱼缸了，Craig Wenger 和 David Turover 这两位美国设计师曾在几年前推出了一款会自动换水的鱼缸，无需依靠其他工具就能在加水时自动排出缸里原有的污水。最近他们将当年的明星产品重新改良，推出了迭代版 GravityFlow 2。它仍然保留了利用水压自动换水这一便利又环保的功能：一旦缸内的水到达一定水位，底部的污水就会顺着管子排出，直到水压不足以推开管子底部的盖子为止。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/930441187/noclean-aquariums-eco-friendly-self-cleaning-glass\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225536BCU7eSjQ1wWyo8ir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225536c7Wtrl9n6CYzd1ow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225536Ui7QrMSXRdFNk14D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.507353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225537tmcyIT4Jw6zWQHUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225537v9Pmfe7RX4aSujzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plane by Plane Industries.</h3><p>我们之前曾经介绍过几个旧物利用的创意，包括用海洋塑料制成的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28219.html\">太阳眼镜</a>、<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28928.html\">筷子</a>，以及用旧足球制成的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28095.html\">腕带</a>，而最近来自英国的 Ben 和 Harry Tucker 则用一系列漂亮的包和配饰让废弃的飞机座椅得到重生。Plane 是 Tucker 兄弟创立的品牌，所有产品均由座椅织物搭配意大利的植鞣皮革制成。为了呈现织物的历史，废弃之前的飞行里程数、曾经到达过的国家数、飞行高度等数据都和订购者的姓名首字母一起被纹在了每个包上，陪伴新的主人再次踏上旅程。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1346754224/a-new-type-of-luxury-goods-made-from-aeroplanes\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，单品价格从 30 到 280 英镑不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225507TWHO9ctiljMm3Jsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225506ekl5A1Wx8mgfh7Ks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225506UQ3COv9AGWR0MVkE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132255073vAB0rhaqnSwxUde.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225506zM7DV6gNiykHFu5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225507LvYHQrociqBaW2Sw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}